{"tid":488398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[殺無赦續集?] 何君堯：要將班友變成太監　批楊岳橋尊容笑得核突","createTime":"2017-12-03T16:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T16:23:36.000Z","uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1d36e6734b79d18d7425fb5d3853e5cf56fdfb","tid":488398,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"修改立法會《議事規則》的議案將在周三（6日）正式提交立法會審議。立法會議員何君堯認為必須修改議事規程，「將呢班（拉布）友仔變成為太監」。他又批評公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋笑容「核突」。<br />\n <br />\n何君堯於facebook直播中表示，希望有關《議事規則》修訂的議案準時於周三審議，強調要「手起刀落，剪布就剪布」，「一定要剪佢布，改咗議事規程，<span style=\"color: red;\">將佢嘅牙剝咗佢，將呢班友仔變成為太監</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，「無無謂謂亂噏廿四，呢啲叫做民主嘅代表？實際上，民主唔係佢專有名稱。實際上，我都係民選議員，我都睇唔過眼佢哋呢啲行為，所以千祈唔好用民主派自稱，實際上係侮辱咗民主精神」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯回應網民留言時又提到公民黨議員楊岳橋，稱「（楊岳橋）講緊嘢時，陰陰嘴咁笑，以為好似好幽默。大佬，照下塊鏡，睇下場合，你嗰副尊容咁樣笑法，實際上係好核突。有時要睇下環境，下下烚熟狗頭，人哋以為你傻嘅添啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171203/s00001/1512287506268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171203%2Fs00001%2F1512287506268&d=0uLJV8DI8brq%2BKz3LwaJakjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=98127e59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171203%2Fs00001%2F1512287506268&h=3f2d5ca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171203/s00001/1512287506268</a>"},{"pid":"ed77b351b824300ddf457ef34f6e75a75afecafb","tid":488398,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281b62cfdbcd3bf5f06fac3ab48f87eb075cfedf","tid":488398,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170919/large/1505835616_8ce2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170919%2Flarge%2F1505835616_8ce2.png&h=bc076695&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}